MDplot.R                         - This script will automatically plot the data from task 1 in R. The commands to run this
                                   script in R are ;

                                   1. set path to the directory where you have run Hermes
                                      path <- path/to/Hermes
                                      setwd(path)
                                   2. load the script
                                      source("MDplot.R")
                                   3. run the script
                                      MDplot.R(path)

NOTE: This script is currently set for windows to use on UNIX systems please change the file separators from \\ to / on lines 6,
10 and 14
